name: Fishy Fishy
overview: A freeware game made by Infinite Gain Software. It would spawn a graphically enhanced version and a sequel. In it, you need to eat as many fish as you can. You can only eat fish smaller than yourself. At the start you can eat only small crabs, everything else will just sap your strength. Boss level is a shark you must defeat by death by a thousand nibbles. Go for the tail, it is the least dangerous end. Six levels of fun!
